678350", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "韩国国会未通过总统尹锡悦弹劾案，韩国政坛将局势将会如何发展？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据《韩国先驱报》7 日报道，在韩国国会全体会议当天针对总统尹锡悦弹劾动议案表决前，大批民众涌上街头举行集会，与此同时，首尔汝矣岛和光化门一带的关键地区出现网络故障和服务中断的问题。报道提到，韩国多家电信公司表示，正密切关注局势，并准备在汝矣岛和光化门等举行大规模抗议活动的地区增加流量服务，以保障通信服务正常运行。当地时间 7 日下午，韩国国会举行全体会议就总统尹锡悦弹劾案进行投票表决。在弹劾案投票进行前，绝大多数韩国执政党议员退场，抵制尹锡悦总统弹劾案。最终，因执政党抵制，弹劾案未获通过。 据悉，共有 195 名议员参与尹锡悦弹劾案的表决投票，未达到必须人数，弹劾案被废止。 韩国在野党 7 日投票前表示，如果弹劾案当天没能通过国会表决，后续将持续发起尹锡悦总统弹劾案。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0eabf7923d17ad0e0629feed1b271078_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6230678350"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIhOCmqOig5/MBEAMaCTExMjIyMjk0NiCAgNG6BjAAOIkCQAVyCjYyMzA2NzgzNTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1733587698.21995", "card_id": "Q_5731561505", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价孟子义、李昀锐主演的电视剧《九重紫》?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-e76b42dabebafa5dc2e775a85a27795a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5731561505"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhOCmqOig5/MBEAMaCTExMjEyMjg5OCDOtbW6BjAAOBdABnIKNTczMTU2MTUwNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1733587698.22247", "card_id": "Q_4820922636", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a